title: Grateful Dead Live at Charlotte Coliseum on 1991-06-11
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko, Walkin' Blues, Jack A Roe, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, West L.A. Fadeaway, Queen Jane Approximately, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime-> Eyes Of The World-> Looks Like Rain, Terrapin Station-> Jam-> Jam*-> Drums-> Jam-> Playin' In The Band Reprise-> The Wheel-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues

*Without Jerry then with Phil, Bob & Bruce

reviews.review_text: Great Show , Awesome mix What a show , Great vibes that night , Loved the Promised Land first set closer, Second set really got cooking , Love me a show with Bruce ! I seem to remember about the time there was an article in Relix about the similarities between Victim, Looks Like Rain, and Throwing Stones , well you got all 3 in the second set here..... wonderful time , from the 1$ Grilled Cheese and Tomato sandwiches in the lot , till the end of the US Blues Encore ! and this is an awesome mix IMHO, Mucho Gracias!
